th.com/mod/sodium)\n\n\n[Armor Statues recommended](https://modrinth.com/project/bbGCtEvb)\n\n\n[Requires EMF](https://modrinth.com/project/4I1XuqiY)\n\n\n[Requires ETF](https://modrinth.com/project/BVzZfTc1)\n\nTixul & Cyber's Glowing Fresh 3D Armor Stands\n\nAbout: Resource pack that adds survival friendly NPCs to the game. Subpack of Glowing 3D Items. Gives a good alternative to people who don't want to install the full pack.\n\nFeatures: \n- NPC models when renaming armor stands.\n- 3D models for held armor stand items. \n- Poseable armor stands using Armor Poser or Armor Statues\n\nOther: \nTutorial for renaming:\n\nCredits: Cyber - Helped make villager item variants.\nKerameh - Took screenshots.\n\n</details>\n\n",
